social_posts.post_text: This is what dreams are made of 💙💙
2022 was one for the books

This tree was such a labor of love 💕 Christmas magic doesn’t just happen, so despite chasing an 8 month old around I decided to put our tree up no matter how long it took. Well a month of decorating later it’s finally finished! I’ve never had my own tree before, so getting to plan it all out was really fun. I loved seeing my vision come to life and can’t wait to enjoy these decorations for years to come - especially the velvet bows that took me a full day to make 😂💙🌲 #christmasdecor #christmastree #grandmillennial
Had so much fun celebrating #sipsoftheseason this past weekend with @crackerbarrel - make sure to pop in and try their festive Glitter Globe Spritzer before Feb 12 🎅🏼 🎄 ⭐️

Happy Anniversary my love! Our hardest, but best year yet. Our moments alone are few and far between these days, so getting a night celebrate just us two is all the sweeter. Cheers to three years!! #sidesmilewedding

Bear’s first haircut 🫠🫠🫠 I can’t believe my baby is almost 1!

#firsthaircut #firsttimemom #firstbirthday #fyp
On the eve of his first birthday, finally sharing Bear’s birth story over on the blog 🐻💙🎂

Giving birth was honestly the most magical, messy, spiritual, exhausting, affirming, heart changing moment of my life. I’ve never felt closer to God or more sure of my body and it’s power. I have a purpose in life like I’ve never experienced. Motherhood is the greatest gift I’ve ever been given.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Happy first birthday my darling boy. I can’t imagine life without you, every day is sweeter with you in it. You have such a curious spirit and fiery determination that is so fun to watch develop. You have already taught me so much, and I just love being your mom.

Mommy’s Caddy ⛳️ We snapped these pics on Bear’s actually birthday which made the day of his party a lot less stressful. I just had @beckleyco come to the house and I used a photo backdrop I got online (we also used it for Bear’s newborn and 6 month photos so it’s been a great little purchase).

Fit details: Bear is wearing a @caddieuniform in 18 month (sleeves and pants with a bit long but we just rolled them - he has a long torso just like mom) & a @waivolstitched hat. I am wearing a @floraisonlane dress in a size 6 and it fits TTS.

Moms Night Out 🍸 had so much fun experiencing the tasting menu at the new @eatstk in Uptown with @adntaylor - it was our first dinner without the babies in almost a year! Thanks for having us ❤️
